Of no help for Black is} 15... Qg2 16. exd7+ Bxd7 17. Bxd7+ Kxd7 18. Qa4+ Kc8
19. O-O-O Qxg3 20. Qe4 $1 Qd6 21. Bf4 Qd7 {So far we are following the game
