2013 White got a winning position.}) 20. Qd4 Qc2+ 21. Ne2 Bb5 {[#]} (21... Bg4
$2 {Is losing due to the powerful} 22. Bb6 $1 Bxe2 23. Bxe2 Re8 (23... Rxc3 24.
Qe5 Rc4 25. Bd4 Rxd4 26. Qxd4 {White’s position is winning but must stop the
last Black’s attempt.} Re8 27. Qd3 Qc5+ 28. Kf3 $1 (28. Kg2 $2 Re3 29. Qd2
